data.description: ARE YOU TIRED OF PAYING HIGH ELECTRIC BILL, HERE IS THE SOLUTION, THIS PROPERTY COME WITH SOLAR PANELS. ELECTRIC BILL IS AROUND 15.00 DOLARS "Welcome Home! This beautiful 3-bedroom, 2 bath home rests in a quiet, well-maintained subdivision, minutes from convenient shopping and the Golden Ocala Golf and Equestrian Club. The owner has made several upgrades to the home, including Stainless Steel Kitchen Appliances, a New Roof with Solar Panels, Energy Efficient Windows, a High-Efficiency Washer and Dryer set, and a Home Security System.  The home features formal dining and living rooms, a breakfast nook, a fully fenced backyard, and an enclosed lanai. The master suite is on a separate wing, equipped with a walk-in closet that will fit any wardrobe and a five-piece bathroom with a garden tub and water closet. Schedule a viewing today and make this gem your Home!"
